title: Johnson has 2 TD receptions, leads Colts over Texans 27-20
text:
> Indiana Johnson has 2 TD receptions, leads Colts over Texans 27-20 Houston Texans' Brian Hoyer (7) callas a play after he replaced injured teammate Ryan Mallett during the first half of an NFL football game against the Indianapolis Colts, Thursday, Oct. 8, 2015, in Houston. (AP Photo/George Bridges)
